    "text": "E-Mail: enquiry@iascertification.com, Mobile Number: +6531591803\nHome\nISO Certification\nTraining\nLocations\nOthers\nContact Us\nEnglish\nService\nIntegrated Assessment\nINTEGRATED ASSESSMENT SERVICE\nIntegrated Assessment Services (IAS)is an authorized ISO certification body with UQAS accreditation.\nThis implies that IAS  is approved to audit third party organisations and is responsible to issue various standards such as ( including ISO 9001, ISO 14001,ISO 22000:2018, CE Marking, RoHS Certification, OHSAS 18001, ISO 22000/HACCP, ISO 27001 (ISMS), IATF 16949, ISO 13485 and SA8000).\nIAS Pvt Ltd is an independent ISO certification body with quite a number of happy and satisfied clients in various sectors such as Manufacturing Industry, Services Industry, NGO, Health Care, Corporates all through India and abroad.\nIAS  in association with its sister concern Empowering Assurance System also conducts various IRCA Certified ISO Lead Auditor training programs in India as well as in Singapore, Malaysia, Indonesia, Qatar, Kuwait, UAE, Saudi Arabia.\nOUR SERVICES\nSA-8000-certification\nChild Labour Any work performed by a child (less than 15 years or any min age…\nISO 9001:2015 Certification\nIAS is a leading ISO Certification Bodies in India provides ISO 9001 Certification ( Quality Management…\nISO 45001:2018 Certification\nWhat is new? It specifies requirements for an Occupational Health and Safety (OH&S) management system and…\nHACCP  Certification\nIAS provide comprehensive support for creating and implementing a suitable HACCP (Hazard Analysis Critical ..\nISO 22000:2018 certification\nISO 22000 certification is global standard that specifies requirements for a food safety management system where an…\nISO 27001:2013 Certification\nISO 27001 Certification is an Information Security Management System (ISMS) standard published in October 2005..\nTRAINING DEPARTMENTS\nFoundation Training\nFoundation training is designed to provide a basic understanding of quality management systems (QMS)…\nInternal Auditor Training\nISO Internal Auditor course is a professional course that is generally a two days…\nLead Auditor Training\nIAS in association with its co-concern EAS does various Lead Auditor Training Programs with…\nOnline Training\nIAS delivers online training through our group concern Empowering Assurance System Pvt Ltd.(EAS). EAS…\nTRAINING FEEDBACK\nTraining Gallery\nOur Happy Clients\n  Previous\nNext\nIAS WORLD WIDE\nGermany\nFrance\nSpain\nItaly\nNetherland\nUnited Kingdom\nOUR MENU\nHome\nSystem Certification\nProduct Certification\nISO Lead Auditor Training\nInternal Auditor Training\nOTHER LINK\nEnquiry Us\nHEAD OFFICE\nIntegrated Assessment Services\nMobile: +6531591803\nEmail: enquiry@iascertification.com\nCopyright © 2020. All Rights Reserved -",
